item.description:
About The Single
Karma's A Bitch (sometimes referenced as "Karma") is the second (scrapped) single from American singer-songwriter Brit Smith's debut album. Karma's A Bitch was speculated to be written for Miley Cyrus but was eventually scrapped and then given to Brit Smith. The song was then later scrapped and was eventually given to American singer and dancer Jojo Siwa. The Jojo Siwa version would later be released on April 5th, 2024. Around the same time as Jojo's version was released, the Brit Smith version of Karma would finally be released on April 14, 2024 after a leak of Brit's version started to resurface online.
